6. Validasi Backup

Cek semua resource yang tersimpan:

terraform state list

Contoh hasil:

aws_vpc.main
aws_subnet.public_a
aws_subnet.public_b
aws_subnet.private_a
aws_subnet.private_b
aws_internet_gateway.main
aws_nat_gateway.main
aws_route_table.public
aws_route_table.private
aws_security_group.alb
aws_security_group.ecs
aws_security_group.db
7. Pastikan Backup Valid

Jalankan:

terraform plan

Jika muncul:

No changes. Your infrastructure still matches the configuration.

berarti backup Terraform dan AWS sudah sinkron.

8. Simpan Backup

Minimal simpan:

main.tf
vpc.tf
security.tf
terraform.tfstate

Bisa zip:

Compress-Archive -Path * -DestinationPath backup-aws.zip
9. Restore Jika AWS Terhapus

Misalnya VPC, subnet, route table, SG terhapus.

Masuk ke folder Terraform:

cd D:\backup-aws

Login AWS lagi:

aws sts get-caller-identity --no-cli-pager

Lalu:

terraform init
terraform apply

Terraform akan membuat kembali resource yang hilang sesuai file .tf.

10. Backup yang Ideal untuk LKS Cloud Computing

Selain VPC dan Security Group, backup juga:

VPC
Subnet
Internet Gateway
NAT Gateway
Route Table
Security Group
ECR
ECS Cluster
ECS Service
ECS Task Definition
Application Load Balancer (ALB)
Target Group
Listener
IAM Role
CloudWatch Log Group
RDS (jika ada)

Dengan begitu, jika seluruh resource AWS terhapus, kamu cukup menjalankan:

terraform init
terraform apply

dan infrastruktur bisa dibuat kembali dari Terraform
